{
  "stem": "523.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Romanian-- the gendarmes were all the time with us, because this was-- Transnistria became part of Romania.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were divided because the Romanian were collaborating with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this part of the Ukraine, they give-- they gave it to the Romania.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Romania use it for one single purpose-- to bring Jews to their death from Bessarabia, Bukovina-- another province, and part of cities of Romania too.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those-- this was-- And the Jews were living in Ukraine for generations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So all those Jews were put into ghetto, death camps, labor camps and the people were brought in-- they were just to die.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the most of us is because we were forced to march from place to place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was winter, no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The clothing those taken away by the villagers or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and that was-- that was life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were dying on the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody would bother even to look at the dead person, because everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If somebody would try a little bit of water to pick up so there was enough, the gendarme hit him over the head with a rifle butt, and that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If somebody had some piece of clothes-- and the-- some of the-- this was already in the Ukraine-- they knew, let's say they could-- a good piece of clothes for a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We weren't thinking for the tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Today, we're hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Today, we're starving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were coming, if the Romanian gendarme was just a little bit farther, we came-- here, you have a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Give me some of piece of clothes or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that time was already snow on the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were eating snow, because there was no water.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
